l(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">Self-Service Kiosks</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; background-image: url(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">POS Systems</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; background-image: url(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">Store Operations</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; background-image: url(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">ERP / MRP / CRM</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; background-image: url(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">Supply Chain, Logistics &amp; Distribution</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; background-image: url(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">Sales Force Automation</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; background-image: url(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">Finance &amp; Accounting</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Retail Systems – </strong><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Network Performance &amp; Security</strong></em> – for this international multi-channel home shopping leader, performed ongoing monitoring, troubleshooting and maintenance of their CISCO networking environment including firewalls, routers, switches, TCP/IP, etc. Established system safeguards, disaster preparedness and conducted periodic preparedness tests.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Marketing Campaign Management – </strong><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Database Marketing</strong></em> – assisted this book publisher and distributor in performing customer analytics to identify the most profitable buyers for targeted marketing campaigns.  Used BI tools, Business Objects, Cognos, SAS to analyze historical purchasing patterns and perform predictive modeleing.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Loyalty Programs – </strong><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Q/A Testing</strong></em> – prepared test plans, created test scripts, performed test execution and reported test results to verify the accuracy and performance of a new loyalty and retention marketing program for an office supply company.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Time &amp; Billing – </strong><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Web Development</strong> </em>– enhanced a Microsoft-based time &amp; billing application for this U.S. based law firm with international offices. Created an adhoc query and reporting system that provided partners and administrative staff with greater flexibility in performing productivity and profitability analysis.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Educational Programs – </strong><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Technology Recruiting</strong></em> – for this prominent non-profit organization addressing educational inequality, provided HR recruiting services to build the information technology organization in support of their goals &amp; objectives.  Assisted with sourcing, screening, evaluation, salary negotiation and onboarding programs.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Materials Management – </strong><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Functional Analysis</strong></em> – provided SAP MM transaction, processing and configuration knowledge to assist in the SAP implementation for this consumer products manufacturer.  Worked closely with internal customers to identify manufacturing related business process improvements with other SAP modules including PP - production planning and SD - sales and distribution.</p>','',1,8,'2013-07-30 01:43:30',575,'','2013-07-31 02:13:01',575,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','2013-07-30 01:43:30','0000-00-00 00:00:00','{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}','{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}','{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"0\",\"show_tags\":\"0\",\"show_intro\":\"0\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"0\",\"link_category\":\"0\",\"show_parent_category\":\"0\",\"link_parent_category\":\"0\",\"show_author\":\"0\",\"link_author\":\"0\",\"show_create_date\":\"0\",\"show_modify_date\":\"0\",\"show_publish_date\":\"0\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"0\",\"show_icons\":\"0\",\"show_print_icon\":\"0\",\"show_email_icon\":\"0\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"0\",\"show_noauth\":\"0\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}',2,42,'','',1,13,'{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}',0,'*',''),(10,46,'Data Science & Analytics Practice','big-data-it-staffing','<h2 style=\"margin: 1.125em 0px 0.6em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; font-family: Oswald, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; color: #00457c;\">Overview</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Project One’s Data Science &amp; Analytics Practice, supplies professionals with deep statistical “big data” analytics and predictive modeling experience. These are individuals who can help companies move from traditional BI historical reporting to inferential analytics and predicting future outcomes. The result: companies that compete on metrics achieve competitive advantage, increase revenues &amp; profits and optimize performance.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 1.125em 0px 0.6em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; font-family: Oswald, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; color: #00457c;\">The Increasing Volume &amp; Velocity of Data</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">The exponential expansion of captured digital data via the web, mobile, video, social media, digital sensors, etc. combined with major advances in lower-cost processing power, open source database applications and wider bandwidth has sparked massive interest across the entire business world in the emerging field of big data science and analytics.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Big data is too voluminous and too unstructured to be managed and analyzed through traditional means. The sheer volume and velocity of today’s data makes capturing, filtering, storing and analyzing it a real challenge. New architectures and products are entering the ecosystem requiring new skill sets and expertise. There’s growing need for individuals who can integrate new infrastructure, platforms and processes into the organization as well as those who can build new analytics and algorithms capable of creating enormous intelligence of great business value.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 1.125em 0px 0.6em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; font-family: Oswald, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; color: #00457c;\">New Actionable Insights for Business</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Data Science &amp; Analytics has application across all industries. For example:</p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; background-image: url(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">eCommerce</strong> – Personalization &amp; recommendation engines that increase sales</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; background-image: url(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Advertising</strong> – Highly targeted, real-time ad delivery to consumers</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; background-image: url(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Media &amp; Entertainment </strong>– Customized content development that maximizes user engagement</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; background-image: url(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Social Media </strong>– Increased site “stickiness”, user growth, ability to track fast-breaking trends based on consumer sentiments</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; background-image: url(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Financial Services</strong> –Optimized lending practices that minimize risk and fraud</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; background-image: url(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Pharma / Bioinformatics</strong> - Improved drug discovery, more effective treatments of threatening diseases, genetic engineering enhancements         </li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; background-image: url(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Healthcare</strong> – Better scoring of medical patients for health risks as well as anticipation and early prevention of diseases</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; background-image: url(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Power/Energy</strong> – Smart grid intelligence, usage efficiencies, energy savings and reduction of downtime</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; background-image: url(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Information Security</strong> – Vastly improved theft detection and monitoring of valuable company information and assets</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 1.125em 0px 0.6em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; font-family: Oswald, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; color: #00457c;\">Data Scientists &amp; Analytics Team Members</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Project One provides talented professionals who understand data analytics and decision science, are well versed in IT, have strong business acumen and possess the ability to communicate effectively with decision-makers.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Our candidates and consultants typically have advanced Masters / PhD degrees in one or more of the following: <em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Mathematics, Statistics, Computer Science, Electrical &amp; Computer Engineering, Machine Learning, Artificial Intelligence, Informatics, Predictive Analytics and/or Data Science.</em></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">In combination with their technical skills, we recruit professionals who also possess strong soft skills and personal traits including: <em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">intense curiosity, passion for problem-solving, creativity, ability to visualize solutions, logic matching skills, positive can-do attitude, and strong communications &amp; interpersonal skills among others.</em></p>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 16px 0px 4px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.125; font-family: Oswald, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: normal; color: #777777;\">Positions &amp; Roles</h3>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; background-image: url(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">Data Scientists</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; background-image: url(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">Data Miners</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; background-image: url(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">Data Modelers &amp; Analysts</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; background-image: url(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">Data Visualization Designers</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; background-image: url(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">Predictive Analysts</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; background-image: url(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">Quantitative Analysts</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; background-image: url(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">Big Data Architects &amp; Engineers</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h3 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 16px 0px 4px; border: 0px; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.125; font-family: Oswald, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; font-weight: normal; color: #777777;\">Databas