.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">Self-Service Kiosks</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; background-image: url(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">POS Systems</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; background-image: url(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">Store Operations</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; background-image: url(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">ERP / MRP / CRM</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; background-image: url(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">Supply Chain, Logistics &amp; Distribution</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; background-image: url(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">Sales Force Automation</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; background-image: url(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">Finance &amp; Accounting</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Retail Systems – </strong><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Network Performance &amp; Security</strong></em> – for this international multi-channel home shopping leader, performed ongoing monitoring, troubleshooting and maintenance of their CISCO networking environment including firewalls, routers, switches, TCP/IP, etc. Established system safeguards, disaster preparedness and conducted periodic preparedness tests.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Marketing Campaign Management – </strong><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Database Marketing</strong></em> – assisted this book publisher and distributor in performing customer analytics to identify the most profitable buyers for targeted marketing campaigns.  Used BI tools, Business Objects, Cognos, SAS to analyze historical purchasing patterns and perform predictive modeleing.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Loyalty Programs – </strong><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Q/A Testing</strong></em> – prepared test plans, created test scripts, performed test execution and reported test results to verify the accuracy and performance of a new loyalty and retention marketing program for an office supply company.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Time &amp; Billing – </strong><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Web Development</strong> </em>– enhanced a Microsoft-based time &amp; billing application for this U.S. based law firm with international offices. Created an adhoc query and reporting system that provided partners and administrative staff with greater flexibility in performing productivity and profitability analysis.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Educational Programs – </strong><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Technology Recruiting</strong></em> – for this prominent non-profit organization addressing educational inequality, provided HR recruiting services to build the information technology organization in support of their goals &amp; objectives.  Assisted with sourcing, screening, evaluation, salary negotiation and onboarding programs.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Materials Management – </strong><em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Functional Analysis</strong></em> – provided SAP MM transaction, processing and configuration knowledge to assist in the SAP implementation for this consumer products manufacturer.  Worked closely with internal customers to identify manufacturing related business process improvements with other SAP modules including PP - production planning and SD - sales and distribution.</p>','',0,8,'2013-07-30 02:33:34',575,'','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','2013-07-30 02:33:34','0000-00-00 00:00:00','{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}','{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}','{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}',1,38,'','',1,2,'{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}',0,'*',''),(14,50,'President\'s Letter','president-s-letter','<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Dear Visitor,</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">I\'d like to convey to you the spirit, the essence and purpose of our company. Project One has always placed great value on the relationships we maintain with our clients and our staff of employees and consultants. Without the combined cooperation and commitment of both, we could never aspire to nor achieve the level of success that defines extraordinary companies in today’s challenging marketplace.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Our clients demand knowledge, speed, agility, quality and cost efficiency. And toward this end, Project One always positions itself as a reliable and trusted business partner, a problem solver and an informative industry resource. The many long-term, strategic relationships we have cultivated with clients testify of our ability to help them successfully achieve their technical and business objectives.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Our highly regarded employees and consultants are among the industry’s best and brightest professionals. They continually look to us for challenging and exciting opportunities, career guidance and development, and of course, rewarding compensation and benefits. In this new era of labor market instability, we remain responsive and flexible to their professional and personal needs. They know that Project One always operates with the highest ethical standards. We maintain professional, yet friendly relationships based on trust, honesty and open communications.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">As you explore our website and have the opportunity to learn more about Project One and our people, projects &amp; technology – I encourage you to contact us so that we may describe in more detail the ways in which we can establish a mutually rewarding relationship.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Sincerely, <br /><img src=\"http://www.project1.com/images/stories/garysig04.png\" alt=\"\" hspace=\"0\" vspace=\"0\" width=\"90\" height=\"60\" align=\"left\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px;\" /></p>','',1,8,'2013-07-30 03:25:56',575,'','2013-07-30 03:26:05',575,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','2013-07-30 03:25:56','0000-00-00 00:00:00','{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}','{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}','{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}',2,37,'','',1,23,'{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}',0,'*',''),(15,51,'Business Principles','business-principles','<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Project One plays a leadership role in <a href=\"http://www.techservealliance.org/\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #00457c; transition: color 0.5s ease 0s; -webkit-transition: color 0.5s ease 0s;\">TechServe Alliance</a>.  TechServe Alliance promotes information and education programs for clients, consultants and vendors.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Project One helped craft the association\'s business principles, the code of ethics that its members live by.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 1.125em 0px 0.6em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; font-family: Oswald, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; color: #00457c;\">TechServe Alliance Statement of Business Principles</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">TechServe members DO adhere to the tenet of equal opportunity for all regardless of race, religion, color, sex, creed, age, marital status, sexual orientation, or national origin.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">TechServe members DO abide by all applicable international, Federal, state, and local laws with regard to the operation of their businesses.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">TechServe members DO NOT engage in illegal restraint of trade, unfair competition, or violation of anti-trust laws and DO promote free and fair competition among members.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">TechServe members DO NOT defame clients, consultants, or competitors.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">TechServe members DO preserve all proprietary information relating to the business of their clients.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">TechServe members DO actively avoid misrepresenting a consultant\'s skills or experience.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">TechServe members DO NOT misrepresent a consultant\'s pay rate, contract terms, assignment duration, or other subjects pertinent to the business relationship.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">TechServe members DO NOT have unreasonable non-competition clauses or unfairly prevent a consultant from pursuing other opportunities.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">TechServe members DO refrain from soliciting employees of their own active clients.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">TechServe members DO NOT induce consultants to breach or improperly interfere with a contractual relationship.<br /><br />TechServe members DO have a clear policy for payment of consulting, marketing and recruiting personnel.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">TechServe members DO comply with clients\' established business practices including those policies relating to gifts and gratuities to client employees.</p>','',1,8,'2013-07-30 03:27:19',575,'','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','2013-07-30 03:27:19','0000-00-00 00:00:00','{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\