0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; font-family: Oswald, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; color: #00457c;\">We invest in long-term relationships</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Our executives and account managers learn about your business, your objectives, your operating environment, your management style, your company culture and how you use technology to stay ahead. With knowledge of your upcoming requirements, we proactively begin recruitment to ensure you’ll have qualified candidates to choose from when new projects start.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 1.125em 0px 0.6em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; font-family: Oswald, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; color: #00457c;\">We quickly find the candidates other firms can\'t</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">We’ve been placing IT professionals and delivering staffing solutions for over two decades, and our network has been growing ever since. Our senior recruiting staff is extremely well connected and resourceful. We often present talented candidates who aren\'t typically in the job market but who\'s interest has been aroused as a result of our ability to passionately represent you and your opportunity. We optimize your time investment in IT recruitment. We carefully screen all candidates, so you don\'t have to. First we pre-screen candidates for people skills. Second we screen for technical &amp; business skills. Third we screen for your company culture fit. Finally we conduct reference checks. Out of a large pool of prospective candidates, we send you only 2-3 per opening. The consultants we recommend will always have the right mix of technical, business and people skills for your specific needs.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 1.125em 0px 0.6em; padding: 0px; bord