le they work for you. On successfully completing the trial period, typically 3 to 6 months, the consultants may become your direct employees.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\"> </p>','',1,8,'2013-07-30 06:10:32',575,'','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','2013-07-30 06:10:32','0000-00-00 00:00:00','{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}','{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}','{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}',1,20,'','',1,6,'{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}',0,'*',''),(32,68,'Project One Events - IT Staffing Solutions and Trends','management-advisory-it-staffing','<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Project One organizes and conducts industry symposiums and roundtables on subjects of interest for CIO/CTO\'s, Digital Media Execs, Enterprise Architects, IT Finance, Project Management, Vendor Management and Human Resources.</p>\r\n<ul style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; list-style: none; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; background-image: url(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"><a href=\"images/PDF/IT-Media-Meeting-Summary.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #00457c; transition: color 0.5s ease 0s; -webkit-transition: color 0.5s ease 0s;\">Meeting Notes from our IT/Media Executive Roundtable</a></li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; background-image: url(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"><a href=\"images/PDF/pmo-notes2.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #00457c; transition: color 0.5s ease 0s; -webkit-transition: color 0.5s ease 0s;\">Meeting Notes from our PMO Project Management Roundtable</a></li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; background-image: url(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\"><a href=\"images/PDF/cto-ea-notes2.pdf\" target=\"_blank\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #00457c; transition: color 0.5s ease 0s; -webkit-transition: color 0.5s ease 0s;\">Meeting Notes from our CTO/EA Roundtable</a></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 1.125em 0px 0.6em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; font-family: Oswald, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; color: #00457c;\">Discussion topics at other roundtables include:</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">CIO / CTO</strong><br />The changing role of the CIO<br />Embracing emerging technologies and new architectures<br />Offshoring issues, trends &amp; best practices<br />Business process outsourcing</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">IT &amp; Digital Media</strong><br />Strategies for monetizing digital offerings<br />Challenges of handling large volumes of digital data (web, mobile, video, social media)<br />Audience research &amp; advertising trends<br />Emerging iTV trends – integrating digital &amp; social media apps<br />Strategies for migrating websites to mobile platforms<br />The digital talent gap – how are companies competing for talent?</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Enterprise Architecture</strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br /></strong>Server virtualization<br />Cloud computing<br />SaaS (Software as a Service) <br />SOA (Service Oriented Architecture) <br />Agile development methodologies<br />Information security<br />Mobile/wireless applications</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">IT Finance</strong><br />Green IT investments &amp; savings<br />Regulatory compliance impact on IT (Sarbanes-Oxley, HIPAA, etc.)<br />IT charge-back systems<br />Calculating total cost of ownership (TCO) <br />Developing sound business cases for new IT spending<br />Benchmarking infrastructure investments</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Project Management Office</strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\"><br /></strong>Mission of the PMO<br />Measuring the PMO\'s contribution<br />Selecting a project management methodology<br />IT project portfolio management<br />IT governance issues</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Vendor Management</strong><br />RFP’s and preferred vendor lists<br />Vendor evaluation and performance metrics<br />eProcurement systems<br />Pricing strategies, volume discounts, managed markups<br />Co-employment issues</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Human Resources</strong><br />Strategies for managing a multi-generational workforce<br />Work/life balance strategies in the workplace<br />Direct sourcing strategies to lower cost-per-hire (CPH)<br />Diversity hiring<br />Creating company alumni websites</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\"><a href=\"index.php/contact-us\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #00457c; transition: color 0.5s ease 0s; -webkit-transition: color 0.5s ease 0s;\">Please contact us for more information on upcoming events.</a></p>','',1,8,'201