 visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">CRM / Customer Care / Contact Centers</li>\r\n<li style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 10px; border: 0px; background-image: url(\'http://www.project1.com/templates/technik/images/bullet.png\'); background-attachment: scroll; background-color: transparent; line-height: 1.5; overflow: visible; background-position: 0px 7px; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat;\">Data Warehouse / Business Intelligence / Customer Analytics</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Headend Systems - <em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Video</em> Engineering</strong> - provided engineering support to expand the R&amp;D Lab environment for testing and deploying new cable television products &amp; services.  This included expertise in DNCS, QAM, MUX, Video-on-Demand, RF technologies, iTV, MPEG-2 and MPEG-4.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Audience Research - <em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Advanced Analytics</em></strong> - analyzed viewership data extracted from digital set top boxes to enhance targeted advertising and marketing campaigns in order to strengthen customer loyalty and retention.  Provided Research Analysts, SAS Developers, MicroStrategy Developers and Q/A Analysts.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px; color: #333333;\">Mobile/WiFi Video Streaming - <em style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; border: 0px;\">Project Management</em></strong> - coordinated the efforts 