Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; color: #00457c;\">Project Managers</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Project planning, tracking, coordinating, status reporting, issue &amp; risk management for application development, infrastructure, engineering, and operations projects.  PMO environments and certifications may include Agile/ScrumMaster, PMI/PMP, PMBOK, Six Sigma, etc.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 1.125em 0px 0.6em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; font-family: Oswald, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; color: #00457c;\">Interactive Producers</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Oversees development of multimedia websites. Works closely with the design team to create visually compelling web pages and interactive user experiences while coordinating with all stakeholders - business, marketing, creative, technical &amp; production staffs.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 1.125em 0px 0.6em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; font-family: Oswald, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; color: #00457c;\">Business Analysts</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Requirements gathering to create functional specifications for development and user acceptance testing. Subject-matter-expertise allows for recommendations for business process improvements.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 1.125em 0px 0.6em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; font-family: Oswald, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; color: #00457c;\">Technical Architects</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Design of the network, systems and applications infrastructure and programming components to support business and operations needs.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 1.125em 0px 0.6em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; font-family: Oswald, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; color: #00457c;\">Data Modelers</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Understanding and defining data and data relationships and how they are used by individual departments/applications and integrated into the enterprise/systems.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 1.125em 0px 0.6em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; font-family: Oswald, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; color: #00457c;\">Data Scientists / Data Analysts</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Deep statistical \"big data\" analytics and predictive modeling techniques for discovering actionable insights that optimize business and operational performance.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 1.125em 0px 0.6em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; font-family: Oswald, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; color: #00457c;\">UX Designers</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Human factors engineering to design user experiences and user interfaces that are more intuitive, increase productivity and provide a more pleasant and successful experience.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 1.125em 0px 0.6em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; font-family: Oswald, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; color: #00457c;\">Developers</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Applications programming &amp; development that consist of back-end databases, business logic and presentation layers. Specialties include web development, mobile apps, cloud computing, client/server, midrange, legacy systems.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 1.125em 0px 0.6em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; font-family: Oswald, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; color: #00457c;\">Q/A Testers</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Functional application testing and systems performance/stress testing. This includes preparing test plans, creating test scripts, test execution, results tracking and defect reporting. Testing may be manual or automated.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 1.125em 0px 0.6em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; font-family: Oswald, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; color: #00457c;\">Infrastructure Engineers</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Support of the underlying technology environment which includes: networking &amp; communications, security, server administration, database administration, etc.</p>\r\n<h2 style=\"margin: 1.125em 0px 0.6em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 18px; font-family: Oswald, Helvetica, Verdana, Arial, sans-serif; color: #00457c;\">Technical Support Specialists</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">End-user support services which includes: desktop support, help desk software support, break/fix, moves/adds/changes, etc</p>\r\n<p> </p>','',1,8,'2013-07-31 04:42:06',575,'','2013-08-01 01:36:46',575,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','2013-07-31 04:42:06','0000-00-00 00:00:00','{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_