g: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Gary is Founder, President &amp; CEO of Project One.  He leads a team of top IT recruiters and key company functions such as business planning, sales and marketing, technical recruiting and operations.  Gary frequently moderates discussion panels and roundtables at CIO/CTO, IT Project Management, Finance, Strategic Sourcing, Vendor Management and Human Resources conferences.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Before founding Project One, Gary was Senior Director of Sales and Marketing at Automatic Data Processing.  Prior to that, Gary worked at Dun &amp; Bradstreet as Product Manager, as well as a Systems Programmer at National CSS.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Gary holds a BA in Computer Science from Queen\'s College, New York, and an MBA in Marketing and Management from Pace University.  He is an avid skier, sailor, golfer and for adrenaline rush - a whitewater kayaker.</p>','',1,8,'2013-08-01 05:39:26',575,'','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','2013-08-01 05:39:26','0000-00-00 00:00:00','{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}','{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}','{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}',1,5,'','',1,14,'{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}',0,'*',''),(47,85,'Ronald Saharyan','ronald-saharyan','<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Ron Saharyan is Managing Director of Project One.  He is responsible for directing sales &amp; marketing and technical recruiting operations.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">A veteran IT recruiter with expertise in IT project staff planning, Ron began his career in 1996 as a Technical Recruiter working for Aerotek, a multi-billion dollar staffing firm.  Ron was quickly promoted to Account Executive where he significantly grew his territory and revenue base while mentoring junior recruiters and salespeople.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">In 1998, Ron joined Design Strategy Corporation as a Sr. Account Executive selling both consulting and managed services.  In 2002, Ron was promoted to Director of Business Development with responsibility for overall sales, marketing, training and strategic development.  In 2005, he assumed branch management responsibility for all branch operations.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Ron is active in his local community where he devotes time to coaching Jr. Lacrosse and participates in various town activities like Clean Community and Spring Clean Up.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Ron is a graduate of the Richard Stockton College of NJ where he earned a BA in Political Science.  He currently resides in Morris County NJ with his wife Mary.</p>','',1,8,'2013-08-01 05:42:45',575,'','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','2013-08-01 05:42:45','0000-00-00 00:00:00','{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}','{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}','{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}',1,4,'','',1,11,'{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}',0,'*',''),(48,86,'Ronald Zander','ronald-zander','<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Ronald Zander is a Principal and Owner of Project One, an IT recruitment and consulting firm that provides top talent for IT specialist jobs. He has held the title of Chief Financial Officer since 1994, when he joined the company.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">A Certified Public Accountant, Ron heads Project One\'s finance and operations functions. He oversees accounting and treasury operations, employee benefits, policies and procedures, and office management.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">From 1978 to 1994, Ron serviced many clients in numerous industries at both Arthur Andersen &amp; Co. and Richard A. Eisner &amp; Co. His public accounting experience included areas such as audit, small business, litigation support &amp; forensic accounting, and special projects.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Ron often speaks to IT industry-related groups on financial matters. He has held several leadership positions in TechServe Alliance, including serving on the board of this national organization. Ron is a former president, and currently serves as Treasurer and Executive Committee Member, of the TechServe Alliance Tri-State Chapter.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Ronald holds a BA degree in Accounting from Queen\'s College, New York. His three major hobbies are \"golf, golf and golf.\" He and his wife live in Scarsdale, New York. They have two children.</p>','',1,8,'2013-08-01 05:46:01',575,'','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','2013-08-01 05:46:01','0000-00-00 00:00:00','{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}','{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\