style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Brian holds a BA degree in Sociology from Bucknell University. Since 1998, he has coached Boys and Girls Travel Soccer in the Mid-New Jersey Youth Soccer Association. When not in the office or on the soccer field, Brian enjoys reading and spending time with his wife, son and two daughters.</p>','',1,8,'2013-08-01 05:50:09',575,'','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','2013-08-01 05:50:09','0000-00-00 00:00:00','{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}','{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}','{\"show_title\":\"\",\"link_titles\":\"\",\"show_tags\":\"\",\"show_intro\":\"\",\"info_block_position\":\"\",\"show_category\":\"\",\"link_category\":\"\",\"show_parent_category\":\"\",\"link_parent_category\":\"\",\"show_author\":\"\",\"link_author\":\"\",\"show_create_date\":\"\",\"show_modify_date\":\"\",\"show_publish_date\":\"\",\"show_item_navigation\":\"\",\"show_icons\":\"\",\"show_print_icon\":\"\",\"show_email_icon\":\"\",\"show_vote\":\"\",\"show_hits\":\"\",\"show_noauth\":\"\",\"urls_position\":\"\",\"alternative_readmore\":\"\",\"article_layout\":\"\",\"show_publishing_options\":\"\",\"show_article_options\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_backend\":\"\",\"show_urls_images_frontend\":\"\"}',1,2,'','',1,5,'{\"robots\":\"\",\"author\":\"\",\"rights\":\"\",\"xreference\":\"\"}',0,'*',''),(50,88,'Stuart Zander','stuart-zander','<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Stuart Zander is a Principal and Owner of Project One. He oversees Project One\'s technology recruiting and consultant relations programs, supporting their involvement in information technology projects, while remaining actively involved in field operations as a Technical Recruiter.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Since joining the company as Vice President of Recruiting and Consultant Support in 1988, Stuart has established and led several Project One initiatives in business strategy, marketing, client support and direct placement.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Active in numerous professional and community organizations, Stuart is a longstanding member of TechServe Alliance. He has co-managed The Open Door Foundation and helped establish The Tender Loving Care Foundation, a not-for-profit organization whose primary goal is to ensure that the Neonatal Intensive Care Units (NICUs) at local area hospitals evolve along family-centered care ideals.</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0.7em 0px 1.5em; padding: 0px; border: 0px; line-height: 18px; color: #666666; font-family: sans-serif;\">Stuart earned a BA degree in French Literature and Business Administration from the State University of New York at Albany. He’s a world traveler who enjoys good food &amp; good wine and apart from English, speaks French, Spanish and Hebrew. Stuart and his wife live in Long Island. They have two sons and one great dog.</p>','',1,8,'2013-08-01 05:55:03',575,'','0000-00-00 00:00:00',0,0,'0000-00-00 00:00:00','2013-08-01 05:55:03','0000-00-00 00:00:00','{\"image_intro\":\"\",\"float_intro\":\"\",\"image_intro_alt\":\"\",\"image_intro_caption\":\"\",\"image_fulltext\":\"\",\"float_fulltext\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_alt\":\"\",\"image_fulltext_caption\":\"\"}','{\"urla\":false,\"urlatext\":\"\",\"targeta\":\"\",\"urlb\":false,\"urlbtext\":\"\",\"targetb\":\"\",\"urlc\":false,\"urlctext\":\"\",\"targetc\":\"\"}','{\"show_title